This is a Nodejs project running with MySQL RDS Database.

Installation Steps are given below
==================================

Step 1 : First, make sure that terraform is installed.
Step 2 : Navigate to dev folder 
Step 3 : Enter required input variables in terraform.tfvars file.
Step 4 : Run "terrafrom init"
Step 5 : Run "terrafrom plan -out=tfplan"
Step 6 : Run terrafrom apply "tfplan"
Step 7 : "terraform output elb_address" to get ELB DNS name
Step 8 : Please make sure that all componenets are created. Now you are able to access the below url

http://<AWS ELB DNS name>/devices

Note : Records can be updated , deleted and added using PUT/DELETE/POST methods.

 